    "perspective_crawl_palette_select": "xim ntsiab lus for the crawl cov ntawv and starfield. Golden: warm yellow-orange cov ntawv on a deep blue starfield (the most Star Wars-like, highest novelty). Aqua: cyan cov ntawv on near-black (high contrast, zoo for kev pom processing differences). Paper: cream cov ntawv on warm gray (lower-stimulation kev xaiv for tub ntxhais kawm who find the bright palettes overwhelming). cov lus qhia: Paper is the right pick for tub ntxhais kawm with sensory sensitivities or photophobia — preserves the engagement of cinematic crawl without the high-contrast brightness.",
