    "perspective_crawl_play_pause_btn": "Hloov the scroll animation between playing and paused. Space key shortcut for ceev hloov. Pause when: the tub ntxhais kawm wants to re-nyeem a kab, the xib fwb wants to interject a lo lus nug, or a discussion breaks out mid-passage. cov lus qhia: train tub ntxhais kawm to pause for their own comprehension breaks — autonomy over the scroll pace is part of what makes cinematic crawl different from passively watching a video.",
