    "pdf_audit_view_panel": "PDF Accessibility Audit — the launcher dialog for the full WCAG 2.1 AA audit + AI remediation pipeline. Accepts single PDFs, batch PDF queues, or website URLs / pasted HTML. Built for accessibility specialists, cov ntawv remediators, and instructional designers preparing materials for ADA Title II compliance, tshooj 508, or state accessibility statutes. cov lus qhia: khiav tshiab cov ntawv through Single hom thawj to nkag siab what the pipeline does; hloov to Batch hom for the legacy-PDF backlog after you've calibrated expectations.",
